    {
      "content": "Dipolar passivation extends carrier diffusion length to 6.2 um (versus 4.8 um for control) with mobility of 113.5 cm2 V-1 s-1 (versus 67.5 cm2 V-1 s-1), as measured by terahertz spectroscopy",
      "content_hash": "192e61d1bb549e4766c2250b64022a4cb0e8126cca2e0dfc758bdf22da3b2fff",
      "declaration_index": 6,
